nitf
Class FileHeader

java.lang.Object
  nitf.NITFObject
      nitf.FileHeader

public final class FileHeader
extends NITFObject

Represents the NITF file header

In NITF, the file header is the first section of a file (before the image subheaders). It gives the reader information about the length of the file, and how many components to expect. It also contains security info and TRE extensions
